OL,3,CFewer exams, lessons on AI and
OL,4,Cmortgages: England's school curriculum
OL,5,Cshake-up
OL,7,FThe government is set to slash GCSE
OL,8,Fexam time, and will introduce lessons
OL,9,Fon AI and budgeting, following
OL,10,Frecommendations from a review of
OL,11,FEngland's school curriculum.
OL,13,FThe volume of GCSE exams was found to
OL,14,Fbe "excessive", with the final report
OL,15,Frecommending key stage 4 exams be cut
OL,16,Fby 10%.
