OL,3,CFewer exams, lessons on AI and
OL,4,Cmortgages: England's school curriculum
OL,5,Cshake-up
OL,7,FThe Department for Education (DfE)
OL,8,Fsaid it would work with the regulator
OL,9,FOfqual and exam boards to reduce GCSE
OL,10,Fexam time, while making sure
OL,11,Fqualifications remained valid.
OL,13,FThe recommendations also call for
OL,14,Fcompulsory citizenship lessons in
OL,15,Fprimary schools, with all pupils to
OL,16,Flearn about finances, democracy and
OL,17,Fgovernment.
OL,19,FCitizenship is already a required
OL,20,Fsubject for those aged between 11 to
OL,21,F16 in England.
