OL,3,CFewer exams, lessons on AI and
OL,4,Cmortgages: England's school curriculum
OL,5,Cshake-up
OL,7,FThe proposed curriculum will teach
OL,8,Fpupils to navigate AI, misinformation,
OL,9,Fand disinformation, with financial
OL,10,Feducation covering mortgages, pensions
OL,11,Fand budgeting.
OL,13,FAccording to research cited in the
OL,14,Freview, most seven to 17-year-olds
OL,15,Fmake online purchases, with two thirds
OL,16,Fdoing so without adult supervision.
OL,18,FThe government aims to publish the
OL,19,Frevised national curriculum by spring
OL,20,F2027, to be implemented for first
OL,21,Fteaching from September 2028.
