OL,5,Cshake-up
OL,7,FA number of other recommendations have
OL,8,Falso been made, including a
OL,9,Frequirement for all GCSE pupils to sit
OL,10,Ftriple science, and scrapping the
OL,11,FEnglish Baccalaureate (EBacc)
OL,12,Fperformance measure introduced by
OL,13,FMichael Gove.
OL,15,FIt means schools would no longer be
OL,16,Fmeasured by how many pupils take
OL,17,FEnglish, maths, science, a humanities
OL,18,Fsubject and a language at GCSE.
