OL,3,CFewer exams, lessons on AI and
OL,4,Cmortgages: England's school curriculum
OL,5,Cshake-up
OL,7,F"It is clear that the (EBacc)
OL,8,Fperformance measures have to some
OL,9,Fdegree unnecessarily constrained
OL,10,Fstudents' choices," the review's final
OL,11,Freport said.
OL,13,F"This has affected their engagement
OL,14,Fand achievement, and limited their
OL,15,Faccess to, and the time available for,
OL,16,Farts and vocational subjects."
