OL,7,FThe DfE also confirmed it would
OL,8,Freplace the current computer science
OL,9,FGCSE, explore the possibility of a new
OL,10,F16-18 data science and AI
OL,11,Fqualification and a new language
OL,12,Fqualification to sit alongside GCSE
OL,13,Fand A-level.
