OL,3,CFewer exams, lessons on AI and
OL,4,Cmortgages: England's school curriculum
OL,5,Cshake-up
OL,7,FThe review has also recommended new
OL,8,Fmaths and English tests to be taken
OL,9,Fduring year 8 to help teachers
OL,10,Fidentify learning gaps early,
OL,11,Fmandatory citizenship in primary
OL,12,Fschools, and overhauling the key stage
OL,13,F2 test of grammar, punctuation and
OL,14,Fspelling.
OL,16,FShadow Education Secretary Laura Trott
OL,17,Fsaid the government's reforms would
OL,18,Fmean fewer children studying history
OL,19,Fand languages post-14 and amounted to
OL,20,F"educational vandalism".
