OL,7,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,8,Fsaid: "It has been over a decade since
OL,9,Fthe national curriculum was updated,
OL,10,Fand it's more crucial than ever that
OL,11,Fyoung people are equipped to face the
OL,12,Fchallenges of today, so they can seize
OL,13,Fthe exciting opportunities that life
OL,14,Fhas to offer."
